Split Tot ==> Train + Test

The model is fitted on Train, and the generalization error is estimated on Test. Here the split of Tot is already provided inside the dataset (= variable test), but Tot could also be split a posteriori, for instance by sampling (random, systematic or any other designs). 

ntest = 30
s = samprand(n, ntest)
Xtrain = X[s.train, :]
ytrain = y[s.train]
Xtest = X[s.test, :]
ytest = y[s.test]
